34
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:47,000
Sometimes the first gift of the night is not sleep itself, but the moment the body stops arguing with wakefulness.

35
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:59,000
Notice how the body may already be a little farther away from the day than when we began.

36
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:11,000
